{"tid":2036029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭像ID審查、半夜禁止遊玩，中國「蒸汽」測試版本悄悄上架","createTime":"2020-05-26T08:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ce5fbf345a9e79086f74a1295f3fa9748ba2c186","tid":2036029,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/8c91f610-9efa-11ea-8dfe-8c27a939f83b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F8c91f610-9efa-11ea-8dfe-8c27a939f83b&h=bb9de115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟牆會有多高？會讓天空只剩灰色？中國這兩年來嚴格加強了網路遊戲管制，可以說是最嚴格的時代，先前就傳出與 Steam 合作推出中國版本「蒸汽」，而現在 Alpha 測試版本似乎悄悄上架，外媒體驗了相關功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/8c67b1c0-9efa-11ea-bdbf-3d1620236564\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F8c67b1c0-9efa-11ea-bdbf-3d1620236564&h=ed4ca065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.遊戲健康警告<br />\n在外媒 <a href=\"http://win.gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwin.gg&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA9lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=12c22e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">win.gg</a> 的測試下，在中國版本 Steam 開啟時，會出現五秒鐘的健康警告「玩家遊玩必須保持節制，長時間遊玩對身體有害」等等無法跳過的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/8c91cf00-9efa-11ea-be55-b9af98d33595\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F8c91cf00-9efa-11ea-be55-b9af98d33595&h=6c1234c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.審查ID頭像與個人檔案<br />\n所有帳號 ID 與個人檔案被修正為預設隱藏，頭像也被改為問號，顯然這部分的內容能公開與否是需要經過中國官方審查，中國版的玩家將沒有隨時自由修改這些內容的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/8c91cf01-9efa-11ea-bfdc-a08fc9d5d73a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F8c91cf01-9efa-11ea-bfdc-a08fc9d5d73a&h=8f2cdf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.未成年認證特定時間禁止遊玩<br />\n外媒發現當他們在當地時間下午四點，中國時間凌晨五點打開《CS：GO》的時候，程式運作了一下並跳出「您無法在晚上十點到早上八點遊玩，請休息一下。」，測試《DOTA2》也發生一樣的反應，尚不清楚這個限制會自動偵測中國時區與否，這些限制在實名認證本人成年前都將會默認開啟。<br />\n<br />\n雖然不知道這個版本什麼時候將在中國正式上架，但可以確定這個系統將只會依照中國政府要求而影響當地，中國在去年 11 月就訂定了相關的遊戲管制法案，包括遊戲時間限制、實名認證與帳號審查等，而 Steam 也積極回應中國官方要求，推出這個修正版本 Steam 平台並正式進入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://games.yahoo.com.tw/steamchinalol-030103988.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgames.yahoo.com.tw%2Fsteamchinalol-030103988.html&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA9lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=bc6ee82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://games.yahoo.com.tw/steamchinalol-030103988.html</a>"},{"pid":"60d1cc5f5a49952f3bdebbf7a8e3f8b576949eaf","tid":2036029,"uid":5475,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"快d 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ff427e43879741a13153db2321730abc749ab8","tid":2036029,"uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"CSGO咁暴力都唔禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d688560dd14cec56ffbd28435c5dfb8542ae6378","tid":2036029,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 金鐘相見<br />\n全民駕駛 以車代鐵<br />\n路面要車 地面要人<br />\n527塞爆港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1ab9e27cc3928d98563e872fbb464ad3b17094","tid":2036029,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a